'''Ôn-tha̍t-màn Hói''' (安達曼海, Andaman Sea) he yit-ke [[Men-kâ-là-vân]] tûng-nàm phu ke súi-thí, vi-yî [[Yin-thu-yòng]] tûng-pet, nàm-pet chhòng yok 1100 [[kûng-lî]], tûng-sî khôn yok 600 kûng-lî, mien-chit yok 65-van [[phìn-fông kûng-lî]]. Ôn-tha̍t-màn Hói ke sî-mien he [[Yin-thu]] ke [[Ôn-tha̍t-màn Khiùn-tó]], tûng-mien he [[Mâ-lòi Pan-tó]], tûng-nàm mien lâu chho̍k-miàng ke [[Mâ-liuk-kap Hói-hia̍p‎]] siông-lièn, he [[Nàm Chûng-koet Hói]] lâu [[Yin-thu-yòng]] kiên ke chhung-yeu [[súi-tho]]. 
Ôn-tha̍t-màn Hói chui chhṳ̂m-chhu vi 4180-mí.
